caption.text:
Every chronicle has its own beginning. Mine starts here, with the launch of a project that sets its heart into the video games’ world entirely. A project of personal reviews about some of the titles that I’ve come to love the most and that you can read on my website (link in bio), while enjoying the visual contents posted here, where I’ll be showcasing my personal collection as well as some inspired art, apparel and décor.

To premiere 8bit Chronicles, I’ll start with an indie game that follows the adventures of a young boy shipwrecked on an island filled with secrets he must decipher, in a meaningful journey filled with mysteries left to discover. This is “Rime”. Hope you guys enjoy it!

caption.text:
Zelda AU centering around Demise’s Curse!

There was a huge war centuries ago, in which the corrupted Ganon threatened to destroy the world. The battle caused massive repercussions in which most people died.

Now they are all being reborn.

All memories of past lives are sealed until a certain, specific trigger awakens them. Once a person has been awoken, they are vulnerable to be corrupted by the malice, Demise’s Curse.
Devastated by their assigned fate, they start to turn into creatures full of nothing but hatred.

Send me some asks @ demisescurse on Tumblr :)

These gadgets will help at every step of life.

Who would have thought. It is really happening. Death Stranding is truly coming out.

This week Hideo Kojima tweeted that #DeathStranding has gone gold. So contrary to what Ryan and Josh believed it looks to be hitting it's November 8 release date.

preview_comments.text: It only kills me that this wep has no rapid fire :(
Attack do not change nothing to sticky ammo, just artillery do. If this build only sticky you can replace it

caption.text:
❄️I'm using this Light Bowgun bc it looks good and it does damage with sticky ammo(Also has sleep and para ammo😉)‼️
❄️I like using this on Kirin but any sticky ammo gun will work on Kirin😂😂😂
❄️I start the hunt with sticky 2 and when they get knocked down I'll use sticky 3 on them (don't forget to evade reload for sticky 3)
❄️If you want Special Ammo Boost, swap the vitality decos for true shot‼️
❄️As for augments, that's personal preference so choose what you like and same goes for what skills you want to swap out or in‼️
❄️As always, fit it to your play style and if you have better decos or gear by all means optimize it‼️
❄️Follow for Monster Hunter Content‼️

🌐 La nuova area di simulazione WAVE PROFESSIONAL TRAINING CENTER, è stata sviluppata accuratamente per un allenamento che garantisce la possibilità di replicare, col massimo dettaglio, ogni situazione che il pilota vive o vivrà nella reale attività di pista e di gara.
⠀
Grazie all’accuratezza dei nostri modelli fisici delle vetture e delle nostre piste, offriamo la possibilità a piloti e team di prepararsi in maniera adeguata al week end di gara, simulandolo nella maniera più accurata possibile e personalizzata sulle loro esigenze specifiche.
⠀
Wave Italy mette a disposizione un Driver Coach che, grazie alla Telemetria in Live-Timing di ultima generazione, potrà suggerire comportamenti e strategie per affrontare un circuito, o correggere in tempo reale eventuali errori e imperfezioni di tecnica di guida del pilota. Una volta tornati sulla pista reale, questo bagaglio di esperienza e allenamento ottimizzerà le tante attività da svolgere.
⠀

⠀
Thanks to the accuracy of our physical models of cars and  tracks, we offer pilots and teams the possibility to prepare themselves at the top for the real races, simulating in the most accurate way and always customized to their specific needs.
⠀
Wave Italy provides a Driver Coach who, thanks to the latest generation Live-Time Telemetry, may suggest the best behaviors and strategies to tackle a circuit, or correct any errors and imperfections in driving technique.
⠀
Once back on the real tracks, this wealth of experience and training will also help to optimize the many activities to be carried out there.
⠀

Dawn of Isles.
Платформы: IOS, Android
Жанр: фэнтези-RPG, Online
Графика: 3D фентази графика
Интерфейс: английский
Доступность: free to play
Занимаемый объем памяти: 1,5Гб 
Эта РПГ очень таки веселая. В игре очень много крафта, от шмота до еды. Постоянно нужно что-то фармить. Сеять у себя на острове. Заказывать в мастерских изготовление различных ресурсов. Очень много квестов. Многие линейные –нажал принять и перс сам сбегает сдаст квест. Некоторые все же придется почитать и попробовать перевести английский. Но в целом мне зашла. Поиграть и убить пару часов в нее мжно. Кому-то может и вообще зайдет на долго.
Всем удачной игры и легких побед!
#игры #games  #game #gaming #mobilegames #rpggames #rpggamesonmobile #mobilegaming #dawnofisles
[Day 1] Hellfire Peninsula
